<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>ClassCasts</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="leaderboard">  
    <h1>프로젝트 쑥쑥오름교실</h1>  
<p>초등학교 5, 6학년 과학 수업 시간에 공부한 내용을 영상으로 정리했습니다.</p>  
</div>  

<div class="navbar navbar">
  <div class="navbar-inner">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="btn btn-navbar" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".nav-collapse">
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
      </a>
      <a class="brand" href="#">ClassCasts</a>
      <div class="nav-collapse">
        <ul class="nav">
          <li><%= link_to "과학수업영상", casts_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "학습자료" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "수행평가" %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "로그인" %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <%= yield %>

</body>

<footer>  
<p>© ClassCasts 2013</p>  
</footer>  
</html>
